title: Dave Matthews Band - Two Step Promo Disc (1996)
description:
This is very rare Dave Matthews Band promo disc. It was relased in 1996 (RCA RDJ-64653-2).

Originally this included also radio edit of Two Step but I don't have it.

Orginal Track list
1. Two Step (Radio Edit)........................................... 3:53 
2. Two Step (Acoustic) (2/13/1996)................................. 6:26
3. Crash Into Me (Acoustic) (2/11/1996).............................5:18
4. Typical Situation (Acoustic) (2/6/1996)......................... 6:20
5. So Much To Say (Acoustic) (date unknown)........................ 3:44
6. Two Step (Album Version)........................................ 6:26

Track list of my relase
1. Two Step (Acoustic) (2/13/1996)................................. 6:26
2. Crash Into Me (Acoustic) (2/11/1996).............................5:18
3. Typical Situation (Acoustic) (2/6/1996)......................... 6:20
4. So Much To Say (Acoustic) (date unknown)........................ 3:44
5. Two Step (Album Version)........................................ 6:26

More info you will found on www.dmbdiscography.com/twostep.html and www.dmbalmanac.com

All tracks encoded in flac. I don't know who originally converted it. I just share it, soucore is probably CD>Flac
